&+WYou may obtain help on any of the following subjects by typing:&*
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        help <&+Ysubject&*>

        &+YMOVEMENT&*         How to get about the game.
        &+YCOMMUNICATION&*    How to talk to other people.
        &+YITEMS&*            Using objects in the game.
        &+YINFORMATION&*      Getting information about the game.
        &+YCOMBAT&*           Fighting commands.
        &+YUTILITY&*          Additional utilities.








------------------------------------------------------------------------------

