In addition to these, many Wizard commands have more options and are more
powerful then they are for Wizards.

%DEMIGOD

&+WDemigod commands..&*

DGOD	- print message on the demigod channel
NODGOD	- Prevents you from hearing messages on the dgod channel.
REBOOT	- Reboots the game without kicking everybody off.
DELAY	- Makes the next reset a reboot.
SOCINFO - Info on connected sockets.
KILLSOC - Remove a dead socket.

%GOD

&+WGod commands&*

CODE                Sets or removes coding flag on who listing.
SYSLOG              Display selected part of the syslog file.
SHUTDOWN <msg>	    Kicks everyone off, disables logins, and displays <msg>
CRASH <msg>         Same as SHUTDOWN, but kills the mud-server as well.
OPENGAME	    Reopens the game after a shutdown.
DELETE [player]	    Totally deletes a player from the system's datafiles.
GOD <msg>           Communication channel for gods.
NOGOD               Prevents you from hearing messages on the god channel.
VERIFY <plr> <addr> Verifies a players email addr for remote mail.









